::KitKat::

She continued to fire back at Shredder.  She watched Stringtra carry 
Quickstrike towards the base.  She drew an ion dagger.  She threw it at 
Shredder.  Then she kept on firing at him.  She was hit again, this time in 
the thigh.  Now her shoulder, her hip, and now her leg were all leaking mech 
fluid.  She looked at Stringtra.
"If I get too many more hits, there won't be enough of me to use for spare 
parts."
She looked at Quickstrike who looked none too good.
"Is he going to be OK. He lookes worse that I do."

She stopped talking and returned fire.
